OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773421880
OL,3,CResidents facing thousands in building
OL,4,Ccosts hope new laws will provide relief
OL,6,FNearly a decade after the Grenfell
OL,7,Ftragedy, the Building Safety (Wales)
OL,8,FBill has passed in the Senedd, paving
OL,9,Fthe way for an overhaul of how
OL,10,Fbuilding safety is managed in Wales.
OL,12,FIt is one the biggest pieces of
OL,13,Flegislation that the Senedd has ever
OL,14,Fconsidered and will mean stricter
OL,15,Fregulation of the structural and fire
OL,16,Fsafety of buildings.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
