PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773421880
OL,3,CResidents facing thousands in building
OL,4,Ccosts hope new laws will provide relief
OL,6,FFor residents at the Victoria Wharf
OL,7,FDevelopment in Cardiff Bay, they hope
OL,8,Fthe Bill will provide some relief to
OL,9,Fthe thousands of pounds in building
OL,10,Frepairs they are being told to pay.
OL,12,FFollowing the Grenfell fire in 2017,
OL,13,Fthe Victoria Wharf development in
OL,14,FCardiff Bay was inspected and was
OL,15,Ffound to have serious fire safety
OL,16,Fissues in its construction.
OL,18,FAfter years of waiting, the first of
OL,19,Fthe work started in early 2025.
OL,20,FHowever, additional issues have since
OL,21,Fbeen found with the roof and balconies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773421880
OL,3,CResidents facing thousands in building
OL,4,Ccosts hope new laws will provide relief
OL,6,FClaudio Trezza, a resident, described
OL,7,Fthe process as as "one step forward,
OL,8,Fone step back" after the further
OL,9,Fissues were found.
OL,11,FHe says the additional work will cost
OL,12,Faround #200,000, which the 41
OL,13,Fresidents of his block as leaseholders
OL,14,Fare currently expecting to pay out of
OL,15,Ftheir own pockets, rather than the
OL,16,Fdeveloper or management company.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
