PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773421880
OL,3,CResidents facing thousands in building
OL,4,Ccosts hope new laws will provide relief
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson for the
OL,7,Fdeveloper Taylor Wimpey said: "While
OL,8,Fwe understand this is frustrating for
OL,9,Fresidents, it is the view of Taylor
OL,10,FWimpey that the balcony and roof
OL,11,Fissues are maintenance issues, and
OL,12,Fthat these therefore fall outside of
OL,13,Fthe Group's responsibilities under the
OL,14,FDeveloper Remediation Contract and the
OL,15,Fcladding remediation works. Taylor
OL,16,FWimpey is not the Freeholder or
OL,17,FResponsible Entity for Victoria Wharf."
OL,26,@yD@gO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
