CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773421880
OL,3,CResidents facing thousands in building
OL,4,Ccosts hope new laws will provide relief
OL,6,FHowever, the management company
OL,7,FFirstPort appears to disagree. A
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "A remediation
OL,9,Fprogramme is currently underway at
OL,10,FVictoria Wharf, led by the developer
OL,11,Fto address historic, inherent building
OL,12,Fsafety matters.
OL,14,F"During projects of this scale, it is
OL,15,Fcommon for further works to be
OL,16,Fidentified once more detailed
OL,17,Finvestigations of the building take
OL,18,Fplace. It would therefore be wrong to
OL,19,Fsuggest these issues arise from a
OL,20,Ffailure to maintain the development."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773421880
OL,3,CResidents facing thousands in building
OL,4,Ccosts hope new laws will provide relief
OL,6,F"FirstPort continues to work with the
OL,7,Fdeveloper and relevant specialists to
OL,8,Fsupport the remediation programme and
OL,9,Fensure the appropriate works are
OL,10,Fcarried out in the interests of
OL,11,Fresidents."
OL,13,FFor those who have fought for years
OL,14,Ffor the building repairs to start,
OL,15,Fthey hope the Bill will grant them
OL,16,Fadditional rights and improve the
OL,17,Fsector for others in the future.
OL,19,FWhat does the new legislation mean?
OL,26,@sD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
